<item>
            <title>[TIKA-47] Remove TikaLogger</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-47</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The org.apache.tika.log.TikaLogger class is essentially a simple wrapper for Log4J PropertyConfigurator.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should remove the class and directly configure Log4J (or whatever logging framework we use) in client code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12379831">TIKA-47</key>
            <summary>Remove TikaLogger</summary>
